  <Summary>Hellboy finds out that the trip to heaven was only a dream when he wakes up.

Baba and Hecate think that maybe their Rogers should wear some pants.

Lobster Johnson discovers a way for them to get something to drink.

The kids have to practice using their new wings.

Hellboy has to pick a new name if he is going to stay in heaven.

Liz and Abe are roasting marshmallows when they get a call from Hellboy, who has found himself in heaven.

Hellboy and Lobster Johnson are drawn up into the sky and learn to ride on clouds.</Summary>
